iPhone Automation Projects

Project: Automated Text Forwading

Problem: 
Important incoming messages needed to be forwarded automatically.

Solution: 
Built an iPhone Siri Shortcut that monitors incoming messages,
checks for keywords, and forwards relevant notifications.


Project: Wifi Network Tracker

Problem:
No easy way to keep track of when and where iPhone connected to different networks.

Solution:
Built an automation that runs every time the device connects to a network. The automation timestamps and records the SSiD, Location into a Notes document to easily go back and read through. 
